2007-05-11 01:42  kelnos

	* settings/appearance-settings.c, src/xfce-backdrop.c,
	  src/xfce-backdrop.h: add 'zoomed' option to backdrop styles. this
	  is a combination scaling/cropping
	  mode that ensures the backdrop image extends to every edge of the
	  screen
	  without messing with the aspect ratio. patch from
	  trondsg@gmail.com (bug 3138)

