2006-11-04 13:13  kelnos

	* src/xfdesktop-file-icon-manager.c: if ~/Desktop disappears,
	  reload and try to recreate it. should hopefully fix
	  100% CPU issue (bug 2160)

2006-11-04 12:53  kelnos

	* src/xfdesktop-volume-icon.c: be sure to catch mount point changes
	  if the volume is updated (e.g. mounted
	  or unmounted) outside of xfdesktop (bug 2489)

