2006-10-13 07:27  kelnos

	* src/xfdesktop-file-icon-manager.c, src/xfdesktop-file-utils.c,
	  src/xfdesktop-icon-view.c: make memory handling with regard to
	  icon reference counting a bit more sane.
	  XfdesktopIconView takes a reference on each icon it adds, and
	  releases it when
	  it's removed. as a result of this and fixing warnings and
	  whatnot, now the
	  icon view actually cleans itself up properly (i think) when
	  destroyed.

