2005-10-02 09:19  kelnos

	* src/xfce-desktop.c: ok, this should actually fix the BadMatch
	  crash. it looks like when i was
	  redoing some parts of xfdesktop, i dropped off the
	  gtk_window_set_screen()
	  call. this also explains why the backdrops weren't getting set
	  right on the
	  windows themselves, but were correct on the 'real' root windows.

