	* po/zh_TW.po: Changed translator's representation in spelling by
	  the request.

2005-09-09 09:43  kelnos

	* src/xfce-desktop.c: remove some dead code

2005-09-09 09:39  kelnos

	* src/xfce-desktop.c: * handle moving windows between workspaces
	  * move handling of sticky state changes out of
	  window-state-changed and into
	  workspace-changed, since we get both signals, and it's easier to
	  implement
	  in workspace-changed.
	  * move the icon creation/adding and destruction/removal stuff
	  into their own
	  functions since it needs to be used in a few places
	  
	  aside from being able to drag icons around, it should be complete
	  and working
	  (aside from the bugs ^_~).

2005-09-09 09:02  kelnos

	* src/xfce-desktop.c: fix handling of icon add/remove when dealing
	  with changes to sticky state

