	* src/xfce-desktop.c: mess with how free spots are handled, and
	  give previously-minimised windows
	  an 'affinity' for the last place they were located on the desktop

2005-09-09 06:54  kelnos

	* src/xfce-desktop.c: fix calculation of next available grid space

2005-09-09 06:22  kelnos

	* src/xfce-desktop.c: * use gdk_draw_pixbuf() instead of
	  gdk_pixbuf_render_to_drawable()
	  * fix bug where unminimising a sticky window can cause other
	  icons to get
	  erased as well
	  * get rid of extra netk_window_force_update() calls, because i am
	  dumb
	  * properly handle NULL return from netk_window_get_workspace(),
	  because that
	  is indeed a valid return value, and not libnetk being b0rked.

