2005-08-11 19:18  kelnos

	* src/xfce-desktop.c: do some code reshuffling: move most of the
	  display-related stuff from
	  xfce_desktop_new() into xfce_desktop_realize(). ditto for
	  teardown: move from
	  xfce_desktop_finalize() to xfce_desktop_unrealize(). it would be
	  nice if
	  people on multihead setups could test this; it's been working
	  fine for a while
	  on my single-monitor setup.

