2004-12-03 05:40  kelnos

	* modules/menu/desktop-menu-file.c: when including menu files, use
	  xfce_resource_lookup() instead of
	  xfce_get_userfile() if the file is relative.

2004-12-03 05:36  kelnos

	* src/windowlist.c: don't use markup when generating window list
	  items; use gtk_widget_modify_font()
	  instead. this way we don't have to worry about escaping markup in
	  titles.
	  (bug 567)

