	  po/Makefile.in.in, po/POTFILES.in, po/de.po, po/xfdesktop.pot,
	  settings/Makefile.am, settings/Makefile.in,
	  settings/backdrop_settings.c, settings/workspaces_settings.c,
	  src/Makefile.am, src/Makefile.in: Added po/*, awaiting more
	  translations.

2003-04-05 00:10  xfce

	* src/backdrop.c, src/main.c, src/menu.c, src/settings.c,
	  src/workspaces.c: Revert last change in debug.h, use "??" instead
	  of ((__const char *)0)
	  Replace DBG() statements with TRACE() in libxfcegui4 and xfwm4
	  because it was generating far too much logs in simple debug mode
	  (use --enable-debug=full to get full traces)
	  Add params to TRACE() (just like in DBG())
	  Remove trailing CR in log messages

